ning through Bellevue University\nFamily achieves success together through Bellevue University\nBellevue University provides real learning experience\nReal learning opportunity for full time employee Tyler\nFirst generation student finds Bellevue University a perfect fit\nDiscover why Nebraska is the perfect place to produce ethanol\nFamily farming for over 100 years\nThe importance of diversity and inclusion in Omaha\nAdvertisement\nTOP PICKS\nDamar Hamlin’s doctors say he has communicated in writing, asking who won the game\nWLWT\n1 HR\nStitch: Generational Wisdom\nKETV\nDamar Hamlin's physicians in Cincinnati provide update on his condition, care\nAP\n1 HR\nWatch: These dogs in Alaska ride their own doggie bus\nCNN\nFriday, November 25 evening weather update\nKETV\n'A major cause of stress': Economy, inflation affecting holidays for families\nKETV\nGOOD HOUSEKEEPING\nShop Wayfair's End-of-Year Clearance Sale for up to 60% off All Things Home\n50 Most Popular Christmas Gifts of 2022\n20 Winter Fashion Essentials From Amazon You Didn't Know You Needed\n6 Sherpa Jackets Amazon Reviewers Love\n11 Best Fleece-Lined Leggings to Stay Cozy All Winter\n50 Best Amazon Christmas Gifts That Ship in 2 Days or Less\nNATIONAL NEWS\nBy REBECCA BOONE and GENE JOHNSON, Associated Press\nPolice: Idaho quadruple murder suspect's DNA found at crime scene\n57 MIN\nBy LISA MASCARO and FARNOUSH AMIRI, Associated Press\nLIVE: McCarthy fails and fails again: GOP stalemate on new House speaker\n14 MIN\nCyclone that killed child in California battering state with winds, mudslides, flooding\nCNN\nOfficials: 8 dead, including 5 children, in Utah the result of murder-suicide\nAP\nBessie Hendricks, oldest person in the US, dies at 115\nKCCI\nBiden toughens US-Mexico border, offers legal path for 30,000 a month\nAP\nDemocratic senator says she won't run for reelection in battleground state in 2024\nAP\nAdvertisement\nHEALTH\nAdvertisement\nJacqueline Howard, CNN\nFDA to review preventative option for RSV in infants, developers say\nBy Jessica Brown\nFirst-of-its-kind MRI machine promises to ease anxiety, save lives\nBy KETV Staff Report\nCOVID-19 in Nebraska: Tracking Omicron, new 'stealth' variant, testing, and hospitalizations\nFlu activity still high but continued to decline before Christmas, CDC data shows\nCNN\nFor adolescents, social media might be a brain-changer, researchers say\nCNN\n2022 ends with looming risk of a new coronavirus variant, health experts warn\nCNN\nOffutt Air Force Base drops mask mandate after Sarpy County reports decrease in COVID cases\nKETV\n'Demand just dropped off': Mass COVID-19 testing sites closing around Nebraska\nKETV\nLIFESTYLE & ENTERTAINMENT\nJIM WATSON\nJames 'Buster' Corley of Dave & Buster's chain dead at 72\nShare\nBy ANDREW DALTON AP Entertainment Writer\n'Romeo & Juliet' stars sue over 1968 film's teen nude scene\nBy Chloe Melas and Nouran Salahieh, CNN\nJeremy Renner shares first photo since snow plowing accident\nAdvertisement\nHere's a look at the movies coming to theaters in January\nKETV\nCeline Dion's exclusion from Rolling Stone's 'Greatest Singers List' sparks outrage\nCNN\nFoo Fighters to carry on, but as a 'different band' after Taylor Hawkins' death\nCNN\nAnita Pointer, of The Pointer Sisters, dies at 74\nCNN\nNick Cannon welcomes baby No. 12\nCNN\nPROMOTIONS\nBy KETV Staff Report\nSubmit your Husker fan photos to KETV NewsWatch 7!\nKETV Facebook Contests\nAdvertisement\nKETV OMAHA\nContact Us\nNews Team\nApps & Social\nEmail Alerts\nCareers\nInternships\nAdvertise\nDigital Advertising Terms & Conditions\nBroadcast Terms & Conditions\nRSS\nEEO Reports\nCaptioning Contacts\nPublic Inspection File\nPublic File Assistance\nFCC Applications\nNews Policy Statements\nHearst Television participates in various affiliate marketing programs, which means we may get paid commissions on editorially chosen products purchased through our links to retailer sites.\n©2023, Hearst Television Inc. on behalf of KETV-TV.